      "content": "talking to people doesn't change the fact that it's just empty. they'll tell me it gets better, but they don't get it. it's not about \"getting better,\" it's just about the fact that there's nothing left here for me. i just wish i could just... stop. stop the noise, stop the thinking, stop everything. there has to be a way to just let go of the weight for good.",
